    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team determined that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient evidence to support the VAD use decision. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed and predictions fall within acceptable bounds for the primary operating conditions. The overall body of evidence, including mesh refinement studies and experimental comparisons, was judged adequate to accept the model for the intended use. Individual factor level gaps were noted but considered acceptable given the conservative uncertainty margins applied in the Monte Carlo analysis.",
